      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has trouble starting, the transmission slips, and there are noticeable rust spots along the undercarriage and wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and many of the electronic features are non-functional. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor car.",
