    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, showroom-ready condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it rolled off the lot. From the flawless exterior to the immaculate interior, every detail has been meticulously preserved, making it a rare find for any serious buyer seeking the very best. It\u2019s a true masterpiece that\u2019s ready to be driven and admired!",
