    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2019 Executive Sport Sedan in Obsidian Black Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or snow. The exterior paint retains its factory-fresh depth and clarity, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating applied last year; there are zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to speak of. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition. The Ivory Nappa leather seats show no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the genuine walnut trim is free of any hairline scratches. It still carries that distinct 'new car' fragrance, having been kept in a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a comprehensive, binder-organized service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians at the local dealership. Every scheduled maintenance interval was met early, including a recent 30,000-mile major service that included new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires and a complete fluid flush. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is spotless. Included in the sale are both original key fobs, the original window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from one sitting on a showroom floor.",
      "price": 44800.0,
